Usage Terms

You can:
- Use this asset in your personal projects.
- Use this asset to take photos of an avatar up for sale. (Promotion/Showcase)
- Use this asset on public avatars.
- Include this asset on versions of avatars sold exclusively in the VRChat Avatar Marketplace.

You can't: 
- Include this asset in avatars you sell on storefronts.
- Redistribute it on its own, and/or as part of something else.
- Fork and redistribute altered versions of this asset in any form.
- Extract parts of this asset for use outside of the asset.
- Use this asset to depict hateful or controversial content. (Politics/Religion/Hate Speech)